            "heading": "Shipping and delivery",
            "content": "<p>Complimentary shipping on all European orders over €200. International shipping available — delivery in 2 to 6 business days depending on your location. All orders are tracked and insured.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row2": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Returns and exchanges",
            "content": "<p>We offer free returns within 30 days of delivery. Items must be unworn, in their original packaging, and with tags attached. Custom or personalized pieces are final sale.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row3": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Sizing guide",
            "content": "<p>Our ready-to-wear runs true to size. For leather goods, please refer to the dimensions listed on each product page. If in doubt, reach out to our concierge team — we're here to help.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row4": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Care instructions",
            "content": "<p>Each ÉCRIN piece comes with a care card. Leather develops character with use — wipe with a dry cloth and condition quarterly. Linen and cotton can be machine-washed on cold, hung to dry.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row5": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The ÉCRIN guarantee",
            "content": "<p>Every piece comes with a 2-year craftsmanship guarantee. If something goes wrong due to a manufacturing defect, we'll repair it — or replace it — at no cost to you.</p>"
